FBIS4-68178 "jptot021__l94044" JPRS-TOT-94-021-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 15 May 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA GEORGIA Armenian Theater in Tbilisi Bombed Armenian Theater in Tbilisi Bombed `Powerful' Explosion Reported LD1505111494 Moscow Radio Rossii Network in Russian 1100 GMT 15 May 94 LD1505111494 Moscow Radio Rossii Network Russian BFN [See "Selected Video Reports" section for TV footage] [Text] A powerful explosion occurred today at approximately 1300 in the Armenian Drama Theater building in Tbilisi. Interfax was informed of this at the press center of Georgia's Interior Ministry. According to preliminary information, there are people injured. No information about their number has been reported. Georgian leader Eduard Shevardnadze has arrived at the scene.
